name: jobless
description: A community where everyone aspires to be jobless and unemployable by making a living off of crypto. In a world where most of us work a 9-5 job everyday and still live paycheck to paycheck, it’s nice to believe in the idea that we can become jobless through our investments in crypto and not because we lost our job. We want to spend more time with family, traveling and learning new things. This project gives us that hope that one day we won’t have to slave for someone else’s business, we will make so much money that we will become unemployable. We will become jobless.
